That thou hast sought to make us break our vows, which we durst never yet,

121
00:09:35,560 --> 00:09:38,560
為了維護我王權的尊嚴 你將接受應得的懲罰
our potency made good, take thy reward.

122
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:41,160
我給你五天時間 讓你準備些衣服和食物
Five days we do allot thee, for provision

123
00:09:41,240 --> 00:09:43,880
免得你飽受這世上飢餓和寒冷或者疾病的痛苦
to shield thee from diseases of the world,

124
00:09:43,960 --> 00:09:47,440
第六天 你那可憎的身體必須離開我的國土
and on the sixth to turn thy hated back upon our kingdom.

125
00:09:47,520 --> 00:09:49,640
如果在此後的十天之內
If, on the tenth day following,

126
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:53,200
在我的領土上發現了你的蹤跡 那就是你的死期
thy banished trunk be found in our dominions, the moment is thy death.

127
00:09:53,280 --> 00:09:55,040
走吧 以丘比特之神的名義
Away, by Jupiter.

128
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:57,360
