晚餐   晚餐
Dinner ho! Dinner!

297
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:25,960
我的跟班兒在哪兒呢 我的傭人呢
Where's my knave, my fool? Eh?

298
00:21:26,680 --> 00:21:28,240
進去把我的傭人叫來
Go you and call my fool hither.

299
00:21:31,760 --> 00:21:33,560
你 你 就是你
Ah. You, sir, you.

300
00:21:33,640 --> 00:21:35,640
小子 我的女兒哪裏去了
You! Sirrah, where's my daughter?

301
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:37,120
不好意思
So please you.

302
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:39,720
那個傢伙在說什麼  把那個蠢貨叫回來
What says the fellow there? Call the clotpoll back.

303
00:21:40,440 --> 00:21:44,200
我的傭人呢?  全都睡著了嗎
Where's my fool? I think the world's asleep. Hm.

304
00:21:44,280 --> 00:21:46,280
他從早到晚都要責備我
By day and night he wrongs me.

305
00:21:46,360 --> 00:21:50,280
每個小時他都要挑起新的事端 把我們這裏攪得雞犬不寧
Every hour he flashes into one gross crime or other that sets us all at odds.

306
00:21:50,360 --> 00:21:52,120
-我受不了了
-I'll not endure it.

307
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:55,680
他的騎士日益橫行不法 而且他經常因為一點點小事就責備我們
His knights grow riotous and himself upbraids us on every trifle.

308
00:21:55,760 --> 00:21:57,080
救說我病了
Say I am sick.

309
