你儘管對她擺出一副不理不睬的樣子
Put on what weary negligence you please.

310
00:22:01,000 --> 00:22:04,520
他要是惱了 就讓他去我妹妹那
If he distaste it, let him to my sister,

311
00:22:04,600 --> 00:22:09,000
我知道他她跟我一樣 不願受到欺壓
whose mind and mine I know in that are one, not to be overruled.

312
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:10,960
好的,夫人
Well, madam.

313
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:15,240
-怎麼回事 那個雜種在哪  -他說你女兒身體不適 陛下
-Where's that mongrel? -He says your daughter is not well.

314
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:17,120
