O, you sir, you, come you hither, sir.

320
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:34,640
知道我是誰嗎  先生
Who am I, sir?

321
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:38,480
-我女主人的父親 -我女主人的父親
-My lady's father. -My lady's father?

322
00:22:38,560 --> 00:22:41,520
我們陛下的奴才 你個婊子養的狗東西 你這個奴才 你這個雜種
My lord's knave, you whoreson dog, you slave, you cur.

323
00:22:41,600 --> 00:22:43,720
請您原諒 陛下 我並不是你所說的那些
I am none of these, my lord, I beseech your pardon.

324
00:22:43,800 --> 00:22:46,680
-竟敢跟我瞪眼 你這無賴 -你不能打我 陛下
-Bandy looks with me, rascal? -I'll not be struck, my lord.

325
00:22:46,760 --> 00:22:49,440
也不能絆你嗎 你這踢足球的下賤東西
Nor tripped neither, you base football player!

326
00:22:49,960 --> 00:22:53,000
感謝你夥計 你幫了我 我非常喜歡你
I thank thee, fellow. Thou servest me, and I'll love thee.

327
00:22:54,640 --> 00:22:58,640
站起來 快滾
Come, sir, arise, away.

328
00:22:58,920 --> 00:23:00,160
滾  滾
Away, away.

329
00:23:12,560 --> 00:23:14,240
讓我也把他雇下來吧 這是我的雞冠帽
Let me hire him, too.

330
00:23:14,960 --> 00:00:04,000
啊 我的乖乖
-Here's my coxcomb. -How now, my pretty knave?

331
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:20,400
-你好嗎 -夥計 你最好接過我的雞冠帽
-How dost thou? -Sirrah, you were best take my coxcomb.

332
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:22,000
-為什麼  為什麼
-Why, Fool? -Why?

333
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:24,360
這個夥計已經趕走了他的兩個女兒
This fellow has banished two of his daughters

334
00:23:24,440 --> 00:23:27,400
賜福於第三個女兒
and did the third a blessing against his will.

335
00:23:27,800 --> 00:23:30,120
你如果要跟隨他 必須帶上我的雞冠帽
If thou follow him, thou must needs wear my coxcomb.

336
00:23:31,800 --> 00:23:33,040
啊 老伯
How now, nuncle?

337
00:23:33,120 --> 00:23:35,840
真希望我有兩頂雞冠帽和兩個女兒
Would I had two coxcombs and two daughters.

338
00:23:35,920 --> 00:23:37,480
為什麼   孩子
Why, boy?

339
00:23:37,560 --> 00:23:41,880
如果我把我所有的傢俬都給了她們 至少我的雞冠帽還是我的
If I gave them all my living I'd keep my coxcombs myself.

340
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:44,800
這頂是我的 再去你的女兒那裏討一頂吧
There's mine. Beg another of thy daughters.

341
00:23:44,880 --> 00:23:47,760
不准叫我傻瓜 小子
Dost thou call me fool, boy? Eh?

342
00:23:49,120 --> 00:23:51,360
你把其他所有的尊號都送了別人
All thy other titles thou hast given away.

343
00:23:52,360 --> 00:23:54,120
只有這一個是與生俱來
That thou wast born with.

344
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:56,800
他說的不完全是蠢話 陛下
This is not altogether fool, my lord.

345
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:16,840
你什麼時候開始這麼喜歡唱歌的 小子?
When were you wont to be so full of songs, sirrah?

346
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:20,280
老伯 自從你把你的女兒當做母親 我就常常唱起歌了
I have used it, nuncle, e'er since thou madest thy daughters thy mothers.

347
00:24:20,360 --> 00:24:22,200
小子 我們要鞭打你
Sirrah, we'll have you whipped.

348
00:24:22,280 --> 00:24:25,640
我不知道你跟你的女兒們究竟是什麼親戚
I marvel what kin thou and thy daughters are.

349
00:24:26,400 --> 00:24:29,840
他們會因為我說的是真話而鞭打我
They'll have me whipped for speaking true,

350
00:24:29,920 --> 00:24:31,760
你又因為我說謊而鞭打我
thou'lt have me whipped for lying.

351
00:24:33,280 --> 00:24:35,760
有時我還會因為沉默而被鞭打
And sometimes I am whipped for holding my peace.

352
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:38,480
我寧願做任何事也不願做傻瓜
I had rather be any kind of thing than a fool.

353
00:24:40,160 --> 00:24:44,040
但我寧可做個傻瓜 也不願意做你 老伯
-And yet I would not be thee, nuncle

354
00:24:44,120 --> 00:24:48,840
你把你的聰明從兩邊削去 削的中間什麼都不剩
Thou hast pared thy wit on both sides and left nothing in the middle.

355
00:24:50,000 --> 00:24:52,400
瞧 那削下的一塊來了
Here comes one of the parings.

356
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:54,800
嗯
Hm.

357
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:58,520
怎麼了 女兒 為什麼你的臉上寫滿怒氣
How now, daughter? What makes that frontlet on?

358
00:24:58,600 --> 00:25:01,440
我看你近來老是皺著眉頭
Methinks you are too much of late i' the frown.

359
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:05,240
不光是這個肆無忌憚的傭人
Not only, sir, this your all-licensed fool,

360
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:09,680
還有你那些蠻橫的隨從 時時叫囂挑釁
but other of your insolent retinue do hourly carp and quarrel,

361
00:25:09,760 --> 00:25:13,240
種種不法的暴行 實在叫人忍無可忍
breaking forth in rank and not-to-be-endured riots.

362
00:25:15,720 --> 00:25:19,400
父親 我本來以為 只要讓你瞭解這些事情
Sir, I had thought by making this well known unto you

363
00:25:19,480 --> 00:25:21,520
就能找到補救的辦法
to have found a safe redress

364
00:25:21,600 --> 00:25:25,160
可照你自己最近的所言所行來看
but now grow fearful, by what yourself too late have spoke and done,

365
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:29,680
你分明是在為他們撐腰 有意縱容這種惡行
that you protect this course and put it on by your allowance.

366
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:33,960
你還是我的女兒嗎
-Are you our daughter? Hm?

367
00:25:34,520 --> 00:25:36,560
我希望你明智一點
I would you would make use of your good wisdom

368
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:38,680
你最近總是心懷不滿
whereof I know you are fraught

369
00:25:38,760 --> 00:25:40,480
動不動就亂發脾氣
and put away these dispositions

370
00:25:40,560 --> 00:25:43,560
這樣實在有失一個做長輩的體統
which of late transport you from what you rightly are.

371
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:47,760
馬被車子拖著走的時候 就算一頭蠢驢也能發現事情顛倒了
May not an ass know when the cart draws the horse?

372
00:25:49,760 --> 00:25:51,360
呼 玖格 我愛你!
Whoop, Jug, I love thee!

373
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:53,000
這裏有人認識我嗎?
Does any here know me?

374
00:25:53,760 --> 00:25:54,840
這不是李爾嗎
This is not Lear.

375
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:57,760
是李爾在走路嗎 在說話嗎
Does Lear walk thus? Speak thus?

376
00:25:58,480 --> 00:26:00,240
他的眼睛呢?
Where are his eyes?

377
00:26:00,320 --> 00:26:03,760
他的知覺迷亂了嗎 他的神智麻木了嗎
Either his notion weakens, or his discernings are lethargied.

378
00:26:03,840 --> 00:26:05,480
哈,還醒著嗎?
Ha, waking?

379
00:26:05,560 --> 00:26:06,720
沒有的事
'Tis not so.

380
00:26:07,720 --> 00:26:09,560
誰能告訴我我是誰?
Who is it that can tell me who I am?

381
00:26:13,280 --> 00:26:14,360
李爾的影子
Lear's shadow.

382
00:26:19,000 --> 00:26:22,000
你叫什麼名字 小姐?
Your name, fair gentlewoman?

383
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,720
-哈
-Huh?

384
00:26:23,800 --> 00:26:27,320
父親 近來您就喜歡開這樣的玩笑
This admiration, sir, is much o'th'savour of other your new pranks.

385
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:30,840
我懇求你明白我的苦衷
I do beseech you to understand my purposes aright.

386
00:26:31,680 --> 00:26:35,560
您這樣一個可敬的長者 應該明智一些
As you are old and reverend, should be wise.

387
00:26:36,320 --> 00:26:39,560
您在這裏養的一百個騎士和隨從
Here do you keep a hundred knights and squires,

388
00:26:39,640 --> 00:26:42,280
全都是些胡鬧放蕩 膽大妄為之輩
men so disordered, so debauched and bold

389
00:26:42,360 --> 00:26:47,440
好好的宮廷被他們的任意妄為攪得像個鬧哄哄的客棧
that this our court, infected with their manners, shows like a riotous inn.

390
00:26:47,520 --> 00:26:48,720
噢
Oh...

391
00:26:53,360 --> 00:26:57,720
所以請您依了我的要求
Be then desired by her that else will take the thing she begs

392
00:26:58,400 --> 00:27:00,680
酌量減少您的隨從人數吧
a little to disquantity your train.

393
00:27:01,080 --> 00:27:04,680
地獄裏的魔鬼 把我的侍從全招集起來
Darkness and devils! Call my train together.

394
00:27:04,760 --> 00:27:07,640
沒有良心的混賬 我不會麻煩你了
Degenerate bastard, I'll not trouble thee.

395
00:27:07,720 --> 00:27:08,880
我還有一個女兒呢
Yet have I left a daughter.

396
00:27:08,960 --> 00:27:12,120
你打我的傭人 而你那班烏合之眾膽敢對上位者呼來喝去
You strike my people and your rabble make servants of their betters.

397
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:14,680
唉 後悔的太晚了!
Woe that too late repents!

398
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:17,240
啊 你也來了
O, you, sir, you, are you come?

399
00:27:17,320 --> 00:27:19,440
這是你的意思嗎 告訴我
Is it your will? Speak, sir.

400
00:27:19,520 --> 00:27:23,040
陛下請不要生氣 科迪莉亞只是犯了一些微不足道的錯誤
- Pray, sir, be patient. - O most small fault,

401
00:27:23,120 --> 00:27:25,840
怎麼在我眼裏變得如此醜惡
how ugly didst thou in Cordelia show,

402
00:27:25,920 --> 00:27:28,840
像一座強力的機器 扭曲了我的天性
which, like an engine, wrenched my frame of nature from the fixed place,

403
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:31,800
抽乾了我心裏的慈愛
drew from my heart all love,

404
00:27:34,080 --> 00:27:36,200
灌入了苦澀的怨恨
and added to the gall.

405
00:27:37,680 --> 00:27:41,160
李爾 李爾 李爾!痛打這糊塗腦袋吧
O Lear, Lear, Lear! Beat at this gate that let thy folly in

406
00:27:41,240 --> 00:27:42,880
這歡迎愚蠢 趕走智慧的糊塗腦袋
and thy dear judgement out.

407
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,040
我的人跟我走
Go, go, my people!

408
00:27:47,480 --> 00:27:52,280
陛下 我是無辜的 我不知道你為什麼如此生氣
My lord, I am guiltless as I am ignorant of what hath moved you.

409
00:27:52,360 --> 00:27:54,400
也許不是你的錯 公爵
It may be so, my lord.

410
00:28:00,720 --> 00:28:03,800
聽著 造化的女神 聽我的哭訴
Hear, Nature, hear, dear goddess, hear!

411
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:08,400
如果你想使這畜生生兒育女 請改變你的旨意吧
Suspend thy purpose if thou didst intend to make this creature fruitful.

412
00:28:08,480 --> 00:28:11,880
剝奪她生育的能力!
Into her womb convey sterility!

413
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:15,920
使她的器官枯竭
Dry up in her the organs of increase,

414
00:28:16,000 --> 00:28:19,160
讓他卑賤的身軀永遠生不出一個子女來使他享受榮耀
and from her derogate body never spring a babe to honour her.

415
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:23,320
如果她必須生產 請讓她生下一個忤逆的孩子
If she must teem, create her child of spleen,

416
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:26,680
讓那個孩子成為他終生的折磨
that it may live and be a thwart disnatured torment to her.

417
00:28:26,760 --> 00:28:29,880
讓她年輕的額角過早刻上皺紋
Let it stamp wrinkles in her brow of youth,

418
00:28:29,960 --> 00:28:33,360
這樣他就能體會到 有一個忘恩負義的孩子
that she may feel how sharper than a serpent's tooth it is

419
