...who, I am sure, is kind and comfortable.

432
00:29:30,280 --> 00:29:32,360
她聽見你這樣對待我
When she shall hear this of thee,

433
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:35,560
一定會用指甲抓破你豺狼一樣的臉
with her nails she'll flay thy wolvish visage.

434
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:40,600
