'Tis politic and safe to let him keep at point a hundred knights!

446
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:25,880
只要他做了一個夢 聽了一句謠言 轉了一個念頭 心生不快不滿
Yes, that on every dream, each buzz, each fancy, each complaint, dislike,

