Ascend, brother, I say.

494
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:40,280
你快逃離這裏
O sir, fly this place.

495
00:33:40,360 --> 00:33:42,160
有眼線告訴了他你的藏身之處
Intelligence is given where you are hid.

496
00:33:42,240 --> 00:33:45,200
康沃爾公爵馬上就要來了 他和裏甘一起來了
The Duke of Cornwall's coming hither now, in haste and Regan with him.

