啊 夫人 我這顆年老的心已經碎了 碎了
O madam, my old heart is cracked, 'tis cracked.

523
00:35:19,920 --> 00:35:22,560
什麼 我父親的教子要取你性命
What, did my father's godson seek your life?

524
00:35:22,640 --> 00:35:25,200
