O lady, lady, shame would have it hid.

525
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:28,240
他和我父親那幫橫行不法的騎士 不是常在一起嗎
Was he not companion with the riotous knights that tended upon my father?

526
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:31,400
