-Is he pursued? -Ay, my good lord.

536
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:57,920
如果抓住他了 我們一定不會再讓他造次
If he be taken, he shall never more be feared of doing harm.

537
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:00,240
