552
00:37:19,960 --> 00:37:23,000
要是我們打一架 看你理不理我
If I had thee in a ring I'd make thee care for me.

553
00:37:23,080 --> 00:37:24,920
你為什麼對我這樣 我根本不認識你
Why dost thou use me thus? I know thee not.

554
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:27,960
