three-suited, hundred-pound, filthy worsted-stocking knave.

558
00:37:39,560 --> 00:37:41,920
你這可怕的傢伙 為什麼要罵我
Why, what a monstrous fellow art thou, thus to rail on one

559
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,840
我們壓根都不認識
that neither knows thee nor is known of thee.

560
00:37:43,920 --> 00:37:47,960
