I tripped up thy heels and beat thee before the king.

562
00:37:50,600 --> 00:37:53,040
我要在月光底下把你剁得稀爛 你這個混蛋
I'll make a sop of the moonlight of you, you whoreson.

563
00:37:53,120 --> 00:37:54,840
